							beach and surrounded by lush, subtropical gardens, the hotel has the aura of a luxurious
							private residence with amenities and service to match. To give you the utmost privacy and
							exclusivity, Ricoh has reserved the entire hotel for our group during our stay.</p>
						<p>This website contains details about the trip, the destination, the hotel and our hosted
							activities and events. As you learn about Sicily and the splendor in store, we know you will
							be more excited and determined than ever to join us!</p>
						<p><em>Please note: you will depart your home city on Saturday, October 24, 2020, and arrive in
